ace-variant\">Verified Routes</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary\">24</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Hidden Branches</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary\">8</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Documented Endings</div></div></div><h1 class=\"font-[Creepster] text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-primary mb-2\">Freak Circus Walkthrough Guide</h1><p class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6\">All Routes, Choices, Hidden Triggers &amp; Endings</p><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl mb-8\">Complete route guides for The Freak Circus. Step-by-step walkthroughs for Pierrot, Harlequin, The Doctor, and Columbina — including hidden triggers, replay requirements, and secret endings.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-surface transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm uppercase\" href=\"#archive\">Explore Route Guides</a><a class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm uppercase\" href=\"#hidden-branches\">Investigate Hidden Branches</a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">All Routes Overview</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">Complete route map for The Freak Circus — main routes, secret routes, and corrupted branches</p><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-primary/30 px-8 py-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">START</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Beginning</div></div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-4 text-center uppercase tracking-wider\">Main Routes</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><a class=\"bg-surface border border-primary/30 p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Main</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Pierrot Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border border-primary/30 p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Main</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Harlequin Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border border-primary/30 p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Main</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Doctor Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border border-primary/30 p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Main</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Columbina Route</div></a></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-center my-6\"><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-2xl\">↓</div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-blood mb-4 text-center uppercase tracking-wider\">Secret / Hidden Routes</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4\"><a class=\"bg-surface border p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors border-blood/30\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs mb-1 text-blood\">Secret</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Pierrot Silent Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors border-blood/30\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs mb-1 text-blood\">Secret</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Harlequin True Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors border-blood/30\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs mb-1 text-blood\">Secret</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Doctor Memory Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors border-blood/30\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs mb-1 text-blood\">Secret</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Columbina Fractured Route</div></a><a class=\"bg-surface border p-4 text-center hover:border-primary transition-colors border-blood/30\" href=\"#archive\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs mb-1 text-blood\">Corrupted</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Null Route</div></a></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-center my-6\"><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-2xl\">↓</div></div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-4 text-center uppercase tracking-wider\">Endings</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Canon</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Good Ending</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Canon</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Bad Ending</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Secret</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Secret Ending</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Unverified</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">True Ending</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">The Complete Route Guide</h2><div class=\"space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant text-sm\"><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">How many routes exist?</h3><p>The community has verified 6 main routes across the four characters: Pierrot Main Route, Pierrot Silent Route, Harlequin True Route, The Doctor Memory Route, Columbina Fractured Route, and the Null Route. Each route contains multiple hidden branches that only appear under specific conditions, bringing the total documented branches to 24.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which route should new players start with?</h3><p>Most players begin with the Pierrot Main Route, which introduces the game&#x27;s core mechanics without requiring replay awareness. However, the community recommends completing routes in a specific order: Pierrot Main → Harlequin True → Doctor Memory → Columbina Fractured → Pierrot Silent. This order unlocks cross-route awareness flags that make subsequent routes easier to navigate.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which routes require replaying?</h3><p>Three routes require replay awareness: Pierrot Silent Route (requires completing Pierrot Main and failing Harlequin True), The Doctor Memory Route (requires finding files across multiple playthroughs), and Columbina Fractured Route (requires perfect alignment across three loops). The game tracks your history using a hidden counter at offset 0x4A20 in the save file.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which routes contain hidden triggers?</h3><p>Every route contains hidden triggers, but the most significant are: Pierrot Silent Route (silence in 3+ consecutive scenes), Harlequin True Route (select all aggressive options), Doctor Memory Route (find 5 hidden medical files), and Columbina Fractured Route (perfect choices across three loops). These triggers are not marked in the game — they must be discovered through community testing.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which routes unlock secret endings?</h3><p>Four routes unlock secret endings: Pierrot Silent Route leads to Eternal Silence, Harlequin True Route leads to Grand Finale, Doctor Memory Route leads to Doctor&#x27;s Note, and Columbina Fractured Route leads to Columbina&#x27;s Truth. The Null Route may lead to Corrupted Data, but this remains unverified.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Route Comparison Table</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">All verified routes compared by difficulty, ending type, and whether they are main or hidden routes</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Route</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Character</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Difficulty</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Ending Type</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Main Route</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Pierrot Main Route</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Beginner</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Good</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Pierrot Silent Route</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Very Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Secret</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Harlequin True Route</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Bad</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Doctor Memory Route</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">The Doctor</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">False</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Columbina Fractured Route</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Very Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Loop</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Null Route</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Unknown</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Impossible</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">False</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">No</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Recommended Route Order</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">The optimal sequence for new players — designed to unlock cross-route awareness flags progressively</p><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary w-12 shrink-0\">1</div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Pierrot Main Route</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Beginner</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">Introduces core mechanics without replay requirements</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary w-12 shrink-0\">2</div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Harlequin True Route</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Hard</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">Unlocks cross-route awareness flags for later routes</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary w-12 shrink-0\">3</div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Doctor Memory Route</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Hard</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">Requires Harlequin completion for mirror connection</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary w-12 shrink-0\">4</div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Columbina Fractured Route</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Very Hard</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">Requires Pierrot Main and Doctor Memory for three-loop sequence</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary w-12 shrink-0\">5</div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Pierrot Silent Route</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Very Hard</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">Requires all previous routes for replay awareness flags</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"archive\" class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Route Archive</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">Complete walkthroughs for all verified routes — with unlock requirements, hidden triggers, and ending outcomes</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Pierrot Main Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Pierrot</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Difficulty</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Beginner</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Ending</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Good Ending</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Unlock Requirements</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Available from start — no prerequisites</p></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Route Summary</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">The standard introduction to The Freak Circus. Complete standard dialogue choices to reach the Smile For Me ending. This route teaches the game&#x27;s core mechanics without requiring replay awareness.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Playtime</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">2-3 hours</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Related Theory</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Pierrot Loop Theory</div></div></div></div><a class=\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\" href=\"/walkthroughs/pierrot-main-route\">Read Full Guide →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Pierrot Silent Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Pierrot</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Difficulty</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Very Hard</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Ending</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Eternal Silence (Secret)</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Unlock Requirements</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Complete Pierrot Main Route + Fail Harlequin True Route + Stay silent 3+ times</p></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Route Summary</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">A replay-aware route where Pierrot begins remembering previous loops. Requires refusing all dialogue for three consecutive scenes. The ending reveals hidden narration about events the player never selected.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Playtime</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">4-6 hours (with replays)</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Related Theory</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Pierrot Remembers Routes</div></div></div></div><a class=\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\" href=\"/walkthroughs/pierrot-silent-route\">Read Full Guide →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Harlequin True Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Harlequin</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Difficulty</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Hard</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Ending</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Grand Finale (Bad)</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Unlock Requirements</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Available from start — select all aggressive dialogue options</p></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Route Summary</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">The aggressive route through Harlequin&#x27;s storyline. Select all confrontational options to unlock her true ending. Contains 7 undocumented hidden scenes that only appear on replay.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Playtime</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">3-4 hours</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Related Theory</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Harlequin Loop Theory</div></div></div></div><a class=\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\" href=\"/walkthroughs/harlequin-true-route\">Read Full Guide →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Doctor Memory Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">The Doctor</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Difficulty</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Hard</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Ending</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Doctor&#x27;s Note (False)</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Unlock Requirements</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Complete Doctor Main Route + Find 5 hidden medical files + Scene 9 mirror visible</p></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Route Summary</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Requires collecting 5 hidden medical files scattered across scenes. The mirror connection in Scene 9 only appears after failing the route once. The ending reveals the circus&#x27;s medical experiment origins.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Playtime</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">4-5 hours (with replays)</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Related Theory</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Doctor Created Circus</div></div></div></div><a class=\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\" href=\"/walkthroughs/doctor-memory-route\">Read Full Guide →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Columbina Fractured Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Columbina</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Difficulty</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Very Hard</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Ending</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Columbina&#x27;s Truth (Loop)</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Unlock Requirements</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Complete Pierrot Main + Doctor Memory + Perfect choices across 3 loops</p></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Route Summary</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">The most demanding route in the game. Requires perfect alignment of all dialogue choices across three consecutive loops. Any deviation causes a complete reset. The hallway gains a fourth door after the third loop.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Playtime</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">6-8 hours (with loops)</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Related Theory</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Columbina Watches Player</div></div></div></div><a class=\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\" href=\"/walkthroughs/columbina-fractured-route\">Read Full Guide →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Null Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Unknown</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Difficulty</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Impossible</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Ending</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Corrupted Data (Unverified)</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Unlock Requirements</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Conditions unknown — referenced only in datamined files</p></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Route Summary</div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">A corrupted route found in unused game files. No character sprites appear. The player walks through empty corridors until the game soft-locks after 5 minutes. May be cut content or an intentionally hidden ARG element.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Playtime</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Unknown</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">Related Theory</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-xs\">Null Route Investigation</div></div></div></div><a class=\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\" href=\"/walkthroughs/null-route\">Read Full Guide →</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Choice Consequence Guide</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">What happens if you choose each option — complete choice consequence table for every major decision</p><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Scene 1 — The Garden</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">Pierrot</span></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Choice</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Result</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Flag / Unlock</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">A — Approach Pierrot</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot +5 affection, unlocks garden dialogue</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">None</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">B — Ignore and walk past</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot -3 affection, skips garden scene</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Missable CG #1</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">C — Ask about the flowers</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot +2 affection, unlocks flower lore</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Lore entry</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Scene 3 — The Stage</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">Harlequin</span></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Choice</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Result</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Flag / Unlock</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">A — Accept invitation</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin +5 affection, unlocks stage performance</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Grand Finale route</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">B — Refuse and leave</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin -5 affection, triggers confrontation</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Bad ending flag</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">C — Make a joke</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin +3 affection, comedic dialogue branch</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Joke ending</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Scene 5 — Medical Tent</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">The Doctor</span></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Choice</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Result</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Flag / Unlock</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">A — Accept examination</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor +5 affection, File 1 discovered</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor&#x27;s Note route</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">B — Refuse treatment</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor -3 affection, locked out of tent</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Medical Failure ending</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">C — Ask about the files</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor +2 affection, hints at hidden files</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">File hunt begins</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Scene 7 — The Hallway</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">Columbina</span></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Choice</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Result</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Flag / Unlock</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">A — Enter the first door</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Loop 1 begins, gentle response required</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Loop system</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">B — Turn back</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina -5 affection, hallway sealed</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Eternal Dance ending</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">C — Ask about the fourth door</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina surprised, hidden dialogue</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Truth ending hint</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">Scene 9 — The Mirror</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">All</span></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Choice</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Result</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Flag / Unlock</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">A — Look into mirror</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Reflection shows previous route character</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Cross-route awareness</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">B — Break the mirror</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Mirror shatters, hidden file revealed</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">File 4 location</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">C — Ignore mirror</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">No effect, mirror fades from memory</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Missable content</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"featured\" class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-4\">// Featured Route Investigation — This Week</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-8\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">VERY HARD — REPLAY REQUIRED</div><h2 class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl md:text-5xl text-primary mb-4\">The Silent Pierrot Route</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-2xl\">Avoid all direct emotional responses during Acts II and III. This route becomes aware of previous playthroughs after the third loop.</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8\"><div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Why This Route Matters</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\">The Silent Pierrot Route is the most discussed hidden route in the community. It introduces the replay-aware mechanics that define The Freak Circus&#x27;s meta-narrative. By refusing to engage with the game&#x27;s dialogue system, the player breaks the narrative contract and forces the game to respond in unexpected ways.</p><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Key Evidence</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-on-surface-variant\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Pierrot references events from previous playthroughs that the player never selected</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>The 4-minute black screen contains narration not found in script files</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Post-credits scene references the player&#x27;s real-world playtime</span></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Related Content</h3><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Related Ending</div><a class=\"text-primary font-bold hover:underline\" href=\"/endings/eternal-silence\">Eternal Silence →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Related Theory</div><a class=\"text-primary font-bold hover:underline\" href=\"/theories/pierrot-remembers-routes\">Pierrot Remembers Routes →</a></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Related Character</div><a class=\"text-primary font-bold hover:underline\" href=\"/characters/pierrot\">Pierrot Character Guide →</a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-6 mb-8\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">How The Silent Route Works</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\">The Silent Route operates on a three-act silence tracking system. In Act I, choosing silence has no effect — the game treats it as a neutral choice. In Act II, the game begins tracking silence choices and removes certain dialogue options from future scenes. By Act III, silence becomes a deliberate narrative choice that triggers unique dialogue branches not available in the standard route.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center\"><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Act I</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Speak</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-blood/30 p-2 text-sm text-blood\">Silence</div></div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Act II</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Comfort</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Accuse</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-blood/30 p-2 text-sm text-blood\">Silence</div></div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Act III</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Confess</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Deny</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-blood/30 p-2 text-sm text-blood\">Silence</div></div></div><div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Finale</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Accept</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-2 text-sm\">Reject</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-blood/30 p-2 text-sm text-blood\">Silence</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">Hidden Dialogue Example</div><blockquote class=\"text-on-surface-variant italic border-l-2 border-primary pl-4\">&quot;You said nothing last time, too. And the time before that. Do you think I don&#x27;t remember?&quot;<footer class=\"text-sm mt-2 not-italic\">— Pierrot, Scene 14 (3rd loop)</footer></blockquote></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">How Route Branching Works</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\">The Freak Circus uses a three-tier branching system. Standard routes follow the main narrative path with binary choices. Hidden routes unlock after completing prerequisites — these appear as new options in the menu after their conditions are met. Corrupted routes exist in the game files but may not be legitimately accessible through normal gameplay.</p><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">The key mechanic is replay awareness. After completing a route, the game updates a hidden counter in the save file. This counter affects available dialogue options in subsequent playthroughs. Some routes will not appear at all until the counter reaches a specific value.</p><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-primary/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-1\">Known Route</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Pierrot Main</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-dashed border-blood/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-blood mb-1\">Hidden / Replay-Only</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Silent Route</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-blood/30 p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-blood mb-1\">Corrupted</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Null Route</div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-0.5 bg-primary\"></div><span class=\"text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Known Route</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-0.5 border-t border-dashed border-blood\"></div><span class=\"text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Hidden / Replay-Only</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-0.5 bg-blood\"></div><span class=\"text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Corrupted</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Route Requirements &amp; Dependencies</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">What you must complete before hidden routes become available — and how the game tracks your progress</p><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Pierrot Silent Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Prerequisites</div><ul class=\"space-y-1 mb-4\"><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Complete Pierrot Main Route once</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Fail Harlequin True Route (select aggressive options)</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Remain silent in 3+ consecutive scenes in Act II</span></li></ul><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Archive Note</div><div class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Dialogue options mutate after the 3rd loop attempt. The game tracks silence choices using a hidden flag at offset 0x4A20.</div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Doctor Memory Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Prerequisites</div><ul class=\"space-y-1 mb-4\"><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Complete Doctor Main Route</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Collect 5 hidden medical files across scenes</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Scene 9 mirror must be visible (requires failing Doctor route once)</span></li></ul><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Archive Note</div><div class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">The mirror only appears after one failed Doctor route. Files 3 and 5 require cross-route awareness flags from other characters.</div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Columbina Fractured Route</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">Prerequisites</div><ul class=\"space-y-1 mb-4\"><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Complete Pierrot Main Route</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Complete Doctor Memory Route</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Perfect alignment of all dialogue choices across 3 loops</span></li></ul><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Archive Note</div><div class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">This route will not appear until all three conditions are met. Any deviation in Loop 2 or 3 causes a complete reset to Loop 1.</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Hidden Trigger Archive</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">Documented triggers that unlock hidden routes, secret dialogue, and alternate endings</p><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">#<!-- -->01</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot Silent Route</span></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Remain Silent Three Scenes</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">In Pierrot&#x27;s route, refuse all dialogue options for three consecutive scenes in Act II. This unlocks the Silent Route branch.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">#<!-- -->02</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor Memory Route</span></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Open Mirror After Doctor Failure</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">After failing The Doctor&#x27;s route once, the mirror in Scene 9 becomes interactive. Examining it reveals a hidden file location.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">#<!-- -->03</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina Fractured Route</span></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">View Ending #11 Before Scene 9</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">In Columbina&#x27;s route, viewing the Corrupted Data ending before Scene 9 causes her hallway to display a fourth door.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">#<!-- -->04</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin True Route</span></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Select All Aggressive Options</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">In Harlequin&#x27;s route, choosing every confrontational dialogue option unlocks her True Route ending instead of the standard one.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">#<!-- -->05</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina Fractured Route</span></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Fail Two Endings Before Loop 3</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\">In Columbina&#x27;s route, failing any two endings before starting Loop 3 causes her to reference those failures in dialogue.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Missable Content Guide</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">Complete list of missable CGs, secret dialogues, hidden scenes, and achievements — how to unlock every piece of content</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Content</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">How to Unlock</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Route</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">CG #1 — Pierrot&#x27;s Garden Scene</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 2: Choose &#x27;Ask about the flowers&#x27;</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">CG #2 — Harlequin&#x27;s First Performance</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 4: Accept invitation to stage</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">CG #3 — Doctor&#x27;s Medical File #1</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 2: Search the drawer</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">CG #4 — Columbina&#x27;s First Dance</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 3: Enter the first door</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">CG #5 — Mirror Reflection</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 9: Look into mirror (requires Doctor failure)</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">All</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">CG #6 — Eternal Silence Black Screen</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 12: Refuse all dialogue ×3</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">Secret Dialogue #1 — Pierrot&#x27;s 47th Variation</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">4th playthrough, Scene 5</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">Secret Dialogue #2 — Harlequin&#x27;s &#x27;You Again&#x27;</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">4th playthrough, Scene 1</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">Hidden Scene #1 — Doctor&#x27;s Precognition</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Scene 7 (before White Room accessible)</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Doctor</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">Hidden Scene #2 — Columbina&#x27;s 4th Door</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">3 perfect loops, Scene 12</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-medium\">Hidden Scene #3 — Harlequin&#x27;s Fracture</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Fail route once, then retry</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/